						<summary>

						<p>Fragmentary. Registers a sale of land to <hi rend="bold">Vaḷavaṉ Mādēviyār</hi> by Śī(Śrī) rāman Kēśavaṉ. The record is dated in the <hi rend="bold">29th year</hi> of the king. One of the fragments refers to Sri-Magadai-kōṉ as a signatory.</p>						

