<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>1st Fragment—</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> pukaḻ mātu viḷaṅka puvimātuvirumpa nilamakaḷ vaḷara malarmakaḷ puṇara Amai
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> tiruvaraṅkattup <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ruḷukiṟa perumā ḷukku vī<unclear>rarāj</unclear>e<hi rend="grantha">ntra</hi>tevar nampi <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>2nd Fragment—</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> tun tan cakkara naṭātti vīrā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> Ituk kovikkina kā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>3rd Fragment—</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> num Uḷḷiṭṭom nāṭṭukkuṭutta paricāvatu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>ma<unclear>ka</unclear>tai kon Eḻuttu Ivai pe <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>4th Fragment—</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> tan varutanittalaivaraik kuṟukalar kulaiyak koṭṭāṟupaṭa neṟitoṟum nilaikaḷiṭṭaruḷi veṅkai maṇṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ya varicaikku Āḻvār kaṉmikaḷ pakkal yāṇṭu Irupattonpatāvatil piramāṇam ceyvittukko <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yārāna vaḷava<unclear>ṉ</unclear>mā teviyārkku viṟṟuk kuṭutten cirāman kecavane <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> piramāṇa Eḻutinena Āḻ <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yiṟ kaṇakku<note n="87-1">The rest is lost.</note>
</p>

